| **Event Viewer** | Windows "black box" — check System and Application logs |
| **Trunk Port** | Switch port carrying traffic for multiple VLANs |
| **PoE** | Power over Ethernet — cable delivers data + power |
| **SYSVOL** | Folder on DC storing GPOs and login scripts |
| **DID** | Direct Inward Dial — phone number mapped to an extension |
| **MFA** | Multi-Factor Authentication — requires 2nd verification |
| **Conditional Access** | Policy that enforces compliance before allowing access |
| **Hot Swap** | Replacing a failed component (e.g. hard drive) without shutting down |
| **Snapshot** | Point-in-time save of a VM — always take before major changes |
| **Veeam** | Backup software for VMs and servers |
| **Mimecast/Barracuda** | Email security gateways — filter spam and malware |

